  m_Name: InventoryIntro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
  - Out in the field, you may find items that can be of use.
  - Fortunately, you already have some standard-issued consumables in your inventory.
  - Press the inventory button on the action menu to view your inventory any time
    during your turn.
